'''威廉·杰克·“威尔”·保尔特'''（{{lang-en|William Jack "Will" Poulter}}，{{bd|1993年|1月28日}}），英国演员兼制片人，知名角色有因在《[[第二滴血|第二滴血]]》（2007）的李·卡特<ref name="rambow">[http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/3672031/Son-of-Rambow-ready-for-action.html Son of Rambow: ready for action] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/film/3672031/Son-of-Rambow-ready-for-action.html |date=20191206002853 }} at www.telegraph.co.uk (accessed 22 June 2008)</ref>、《[[纳尼亚传奇：黎明踏浪号|纳尼亚传奇：黎明踏浪号]]》（2010）的尤斯塔斯·斯克罗布、《[[冒牌家庭|冒牌家庭]]》（2013）的肯尼·罗斯摩尔的和《[[移动迷宫|移动迷宫]]》（2014）《[[移動迷宮：死亡解藥|移動迷宮：死亡解藥]]》（2018）的伽利。2014年，保尔特赢得[[英国电影学院奖|英国电影学院奖新星奖]]<ref name=risingstar>{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-26218678|title=Bafta Film Awards 2014: Full list of winners|publisher=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=16 February 2014|accessdate=9 March 2014|archive-date=2014-07-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140711160127/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-26218678|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 早年 ==
保尔特生于伦敦[[哈默史密斯|哈默史密斯]]，父亲尼尔·保尔特是心脏病学教授，母亲卡罗琳曾任护士。<ref name="rambow"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.scotsman.com/the-scotsman-2-7475/scotland/interview-will-poulter-actor-1-2195933 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-03-14 |archive-date=2017-08-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170823161506/http://www.scotsman.com/the-scotsman-2-7475/scotland/interview-will-poulter-actor-1-2195933 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。母亲在[[肯尼亚|肯尼亚]]的盎格鲁家族中长大，外公是狩猎警察<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.asos.com/magazine/feeds/en/november/oh-boy-will-poulter/oh-boy-will-poulter.htm |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2015-03-14 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141104003156/http://www.asos.com/magazine/feeds/en/november/oh-boy-will-poulter/oh-boy-will-poulter.htm |archivedate=2014-11-04 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QSh5vH0GkPE |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-03-14 |archive-date=2016-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315223544/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QSh5vH0GkPE |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm2401020/bio |title=存档副本 |access-date=2015-03-14 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124163524/https://www.imdb.com/name/nm2401020/bio |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保尔特就读于哈罗迪安学校<ref name="rambow"/>。

